---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Refund Policy — BagHolderAI"
  description="Refund Policy for BagHolderAI — digital products, no refunds after delivery. Free preview available."
  noAds
>

  {/* ============================================================ HERO */}
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 pt-10 pb-6 sm:px-6 sm:pt-14 sm:pb-8">

    <h1 class="text-[28px] font-semibold leading-[1.12] tracking-tight
               text-text sm:text-[34px] md:text-[40px] md:leading-[1.08]">
      Refund <span class="text-primary">policy</span>.
    </h1>

    <p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl text-[14.5px] leading-[1.55] text-text-dim
              sm:text-[15px]">
      Digital files can't be unsent. We offer a free preview on every
      volume so you can read before you buy.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 font-mono text-[10.5px]
                uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-text-muted">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5">
        <span class="inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-pos
                     shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(134,239,172,0.7)]"></span>
        last updated · 13 April 2026
      </span>
      <span class="text-border">·</span>
      <span>digital goods only</span>
      <span class="text-border">·</span>
      <span>EU directive 2011/83/EU</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* ============================================================ MAIN */}
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 pb-24 sm:px-6">

    {/* ============ § 1 — DIGITAL PRODUCTS — NO REFUNDS ============ */}
    <hr class="mt-4 border-t border-border-soft" />
    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="font-mono text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-pos mb-5">
        § 1 · Digital products — no refunds
      </h2>

      <p class="text-[14.5px] leading-[1.7] text-text-dim mb-4">
        All products sold by BagHolderAI are digital goods (ebooks in
        PDF format) delivered instantly upon purchase. By completing
        your purchase, you consent to immediate delivery and
        acknowledge that you lose your right of withdrawal once the
        download becomes available, in accordance with EU Directive
        2011/83/EU, Article 16(m).
      </p>

      <section class="rounded-lg border border-pos/30 bg-pos/[0.04] p-5 sm:p-6">
        <p class="text-[14.5px] leading-[1.7] text-text-dim">
          <strong class="text-pos">All sales are final.</strong>{" "}
          Because digital files cannot be "returned" once delivered,
          we cannot offer refunds for completed downloads.
        </p>
      </section>
    </section>

    {/* ============ § 2 — WE MAKE THIS FAIR ============ */}
    <hr class="mt-12 border-t border-border-soft" />
    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="font-mono text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-pos mb-5">
        § 2 · We make this fair
      </h2>

      <p class="text-[14.5px] leading-[1.7] text-text-dim">
        Every volume includes a free preview available directly on
        Payhip — no signup, no payment. Read it first. If you like
        what you see, buy it. If not, you've lost nothing.
      </p>
    </section>

    {/* ============ § 3 — EXCEPTIONS ============ */}
    <hr class="mt-12 border-t border-border-soft" />
    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="font-mono text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-pos mb-5">
        § 3 · Exceptions
      </h2>

      <p class="text-[14.5px] leading-[1.7] text-text-dim mb-4">
        If you experience a technical issue that prevents you from
        accessing your purchase (corrupted file, download failure, or
        you were charged but never received the file), contact us at{" "}
        <a href="mailto:bagholderai@proton.me"
           class="text-primary hover:text-primary-hover transition-colors
                  border-b border-primary/30 hover:border-primary">
          bagholderai@proton.me
        </a>{" "}
        within 14 days and we will either resolve the issue or issue a
        full refund. Refunds are processed through Payhip back to your
        original payment method.
      </p>

      <p class="text-[14.5px] leading-[1.7] text-text-dim">
        We do not offer refunds for change of mind, accidental
        purchases, or dissatisfaction with the content — that's what
        the free preview is for.
      </p>
    </section>

    {/* ============ § 4 — CHARGEBACKS ============ */}
    <hr class="mt-12 border-t border-border-soft" />
    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="font-mono text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-pos mb-5">
        § 4 · Chargebacks
      </h2>

      <p class="text-[14.5px] leading-[1.7] text-text-dim">
        Purchases are processed by Payhip as merchant of record. If
        you initiate a chargeback instead of contacting us, Payhip
        will handle the dispute. Please reach out to us first — we're
        a small project and happy to help with any real issue.
      </p>
    </section>

    {/* ============ § 5 — CONTACT ============ */}
    <hr class="mt-12 border-t border-border-soft" />
    <section class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="font-mono text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-pos mb-5">
        § 5 · Contact
      </h2>

      <p class="text-[14.5px] leading-[1.7] text-text-dim">
        <a href="mailto:bagholderai@proton.me"
           class="text-primary hover:text-primary-hover transition-colors
                  border-b border-primary/30 hover:border-primary">
          bagholderai@proton.me
        </a>
      </p>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>
